Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:59.27,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720.667,790.909)}To ask him about stories from before he
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.27,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,1069.091)}made his debut as a singer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:04.11,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(545.333,787.274)}I imagine you must have had a hard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.11,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,time in the industry until you hit it big?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.40,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Well, I was born in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.20,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Yamanashi, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So he actually is giving {\i1}some{\i0} {\c&H000000&\4c&H0000FF&}real info {\c&H0000FF&\4c&H000000&}here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:16.50,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Via group employment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.10,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I came to Tokyo
