Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:24.23,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,You were 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b0\fscx55.733\fscy63\pos(432,333.818)}*'Group Employment', or 集団就職, was a system of finding work \N wherein unemployed graduates (usually of Junior High Schools) \N would come to urban areas for employment of varying quality. \N It seems to have been more prevalent in the decades just after WWII.{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.43,Hamada,,0,0,0,,20 is definitely late, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.26,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He should've been in his teens back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.96,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the middle, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Apparently he started working after Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:32.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's not what he said at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.97,0:06:35.24,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\fade(400,0)}{\blur6.818}Ah, well...{\alpha&HFF&}anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.94,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Ah, well...anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.38,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}You have to support{\alpha&HFF&} your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.31,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}You have to support your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:45.66,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And you weren't married back then, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.19,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I just mean the family from before I got married-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.75,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}the family that raised me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So who, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:56.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Do you have any siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.59,0:06:56.73,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(1105.334,690.91)}Oh, as for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.73,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(1105.334,800)}I do have some, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.10,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.73,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,{\fscx140.067\fscy135}Actually tell us about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Sisters? Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:03.00,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}I had an older sister as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.33,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Yes, an older sister.
