Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.81,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So, in the beginning-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:09.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,How about a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:13.85,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.333,912.727)}Did you ever own a dog or anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.85,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}A dog, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:18.58,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(721.333,838.181)}It's not like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:18.58,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}"Let's get a dog" or anything, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.25,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}there certainly was one.
