Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.56,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(1181.333,664.546)}Pera...{\alpha&HFF&}Pera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Pera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:34.10,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(1181.333,664.546)}Pera...Pera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.27,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It was called Pera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:36.93,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So you had two dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:39.14,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818\pos(722,935.455)}There was Pera and there was Bera, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.20,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,He had two?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:39.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see, two dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.91,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721,901.364)}Who debuted around the same time as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.54,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}At that time...
