Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:46.68,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}There was Ikuzoh, Yoshi Ikuzoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:50.05,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722,909.091)}That's definitely not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah that can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:54.49,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His debut was a bit later, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.85,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Well actually, most of them{\alpha&HFF&} are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:59.12,Mori Shinichi Endo,,0,0,0,,{\blur6.818}Well actually, most of them are already dead.
